{
  "prompt": "An inventory management app. Products have a name, a unique SKU and a unit price. Warehouses have a name and a location. Stock movements reference a product and a warehouse and record a quantity, a movement type of inbound, outbound or adjustment, and a movement date. Lists for products, warehouses and stock movements, with a form for each.",
